@node Main "Bordo - Documentation"

                                Bordo 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Bordo' is a game @{" played " link play} on an 8 by 8 tiles board; the center 6 by 6
tiles area is occupied by coloured tiles and the border tiles on the board
have triangular shaped icons that are used to move coloured tiles. The idea
is to align 3 tiles or more of the same colour on the border tiles of the
game board. The tiles may be placed horizontally, vertically or both.

  Have fun!

